Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.65,0:00:04.15,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS}FLYING IN THE SKY
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.22,0:00:09.09,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最高的地方 馳騁於空中的任何角落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.53,0:00:10.82,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS}SHINING FINGER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.05,0:00:12.80,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃耀著光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.79,0:00:16.22,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照亮大地的盡頭呼喚奇跡的咒語 {\fnComic Sans MS}SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.68,0:00:25.34,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫不遲疑的前進
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.66,0:00:31.62,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有無限的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.53,0:00:39.08,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論嘗試多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.48,0:00:47.41,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論多麼痛苦都貫徹到底{\fnComic Sans MS}（G GUNDAM）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.47,0:00:50.53,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛隨時都充斥於這胸中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.72,0:00:54.11,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠不會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.13,0:00:57.22,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這雙手 咆哮著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:01:01.21,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向明天飛奔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.30,0:01:03.00,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS}BRIGHT YOU NOW
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.65,0:01:07.96,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所描繪的未來之藍圖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.30,0:01:09.70,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS}SHINING FINGER
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.83,0:01:11.50,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.50,0:01:15.24,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部如你所願 {\fnComic Sans MS}I GET A CHANCE！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下來！你不可飛越國境！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.83,0:01:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我警告你！停下來！馬上停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.24,0:01:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一日，一艘穿梭機衝過宇宙的\Nneo France國境飛落地球
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.58,0:01:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的地是基亞拿高地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.02,0:02:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而目標竟然是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.82,0:02:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同屬neo France的喬爾殊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.03,0:02:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,局勢風起雲湧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.86,0:02:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日的對手是執著的戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.70,0:02:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尚·皮亞爾·米拿保
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.80,0:02:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，GUNDAM FIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs56}喬爾殊！粉碎惡夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.19,0:02:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了，雷蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.93,0:02:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你畢竟不是我對手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我雷蒙好歹也當了山度家的管家45年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還未輸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.40,0:02:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還未輸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.35,0:02:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬爾殊少爺，你不要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.98,0:03:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起初教你劍術的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我說過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.53,0:03:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你永遠當我是小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了？喬爾殊少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬爾殊少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來…！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.38,0:03:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬爾殊少爺！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來！別過來！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬爾殊少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.69,0:03:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你冷靜一點！喬爾殊少爺！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.09,0:03:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Rose！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有病？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.14,0:03:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:04:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬爾殊少爺他最近精神不振
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練習也像剛才一樣心不在焉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.41,0:04:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.15,0:04:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你替他診斷一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還不住口，雷蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，管家他自以為是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我不會介意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，你不用擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，你剛才出現的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得太巧合了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你們兩人約好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記起有件事要辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.35,0:04:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狡猾！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.92,0:04:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說中了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然不事先請示我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽聞多蒙先生的修練也停滯不前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是，我想你們兩人合力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.24,0:05:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便會找到辦法突破自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了！退下！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，究竟怎辦才能把SUPER MODE運用自如？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:05:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.09,0:06:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然厲害，多蒙·卡休先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.66,0:06:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避得好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.33,0:06:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是neo France的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.94,0:06:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我前來是有事跟你商量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.34,0:06:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事商量？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是為了我主人喬爾殊少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.79,0:06:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去了哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我，雷蒙！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉艾蕾殿下！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉艾蕾殿…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.16,0:07:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉艾蕾殿下！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那個夢…！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是GUNDAM FIGHT的資料檔案嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.80,0:07:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，這記錄了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬爾殊少爺的所有戰鬥資料
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.54,0:07:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給他知道你拿了出來會不得了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.81,0:07:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:07:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:08:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也全因我關心喬爾殊少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.38,0:08:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是喬爾殊少爺最近進行FIGHT的情形
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真的是那個喬爾殊嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.01,0:08:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直好像被什麼東西附體一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.64,0:08:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實這是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，大約一年之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.22,0:08:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時正舉行neo France的Gundam Fighter選拔賽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想臨陣退縮嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，玫瑰浮游炮！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬爾殊少爺的對手是米拿保
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他背向觀眾席
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.44,0:08:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令Gundam Rose不能使用武器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.54,0:09:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已束手無策
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑…卑鄙！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是勝利啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.59,0:09:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米拿保！你那種卑鄙手段
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.06,0:09:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令我看的不爽！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此，我決定由喬爾殊·山度
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出任我國的Gundam Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.64,0:09:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.91,0:09:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬賽的悲劇，我曾聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米拿保雖然保住性命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但因叛國罪被判一千年徒刑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而喬爾殊少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.69,0:10:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直也想忘掉這件事，但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇上Devil Gundam的打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次挑起他心底的創傷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，你想我做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你引導他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以GUNDAM FIGHT去引導喬爾殊少爺迷惘的靈魂…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那必要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬爾殊少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的對話我全部聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到你會違背我的話到這地步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.99,0:10:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以neo France的Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.16,0:11:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我以山度家的雷蒙·彼索解雇你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬…喬爾殊少爺…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當了管家45年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連喬爾殊少爺的尿布也換過…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.20,0:11:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然被解雇…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.04,0:11:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆！再來一杯咖啡！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管喬爾殊他們的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那和我們無關
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.62,0:12:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你或許意外地得到別人的愛戴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不只喬爾殊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.39,0:12:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連奇波迪、蔡齋西和阿魯哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也倚賴你而來到這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倚賴我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子漢間的友情真是令人羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.14,0:12:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼下一宗新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年前於neo France衛星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導致馬賽的悲劇而被叛徒刑的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.98,0:12:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尚·皮亞爾·米拿保逃獄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急在地球降落
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.69,0:12:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米拿保逃出衛星時
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.99,0:12:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪去被扣押的GUNDAM…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.49,0:12:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.53,0:12:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬爾殊少爺！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晨光令人神清氣爽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.13,0:12:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也無法消除我的惡夢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.74,0:12:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.34,0:12:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是雀鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬爾殊少爺，茶沖好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些紅玫瑰如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬爾殊少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.37,0:13:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨好！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.27,0:13:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.27,0:13:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙·卡休！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙先生真的走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.15,0:13:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辱沒了山度家的傢伙沒資格回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辱沒了山度家名聲的不是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為區區Devil Gundam的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便喪失自己騎士道精神的膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.66,0:13:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒資格稱為Gundam Fighter！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，你或許講得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我害怕操縱GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.47,0:13:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬爾殊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.91,0:14:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久不見了，喬爾殊·山度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那聲音是米拿保！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決一死戰吧！喬爾殊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管，這是喬爾殊的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一年真漫長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你奪去我的代表寶座，我要報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.59,0:14:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來，誰有資格當Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次就來分個高下吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公子哥兒！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.46,0:14:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我被解雇了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:15:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不該離開你身邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬爾殊少爺！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難…難道…太遲了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.94,0:15:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著，我要打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為neo France的代表！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬爾殊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.86,0:15:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣收拾你！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.16,0:16:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SHINING FINGER！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒柏茲·布魯達！又是你嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何阻止我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.31,0:16:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別出手，這是他的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.78,0:16:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬爾殊·山度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你也擁有撒夫爾的信物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它應該有答案給你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.66,0:16:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.46,0:16:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個廢物！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.33,0:16:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再生了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙被DG細胞感染了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，我降落地球時遇上Master Asia
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我就把靈魂賣了給魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.01,0:16:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓你們見識
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.35,0:16:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了報仇而得到的這力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧！給我死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.87,0:17:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的飛彈用不完的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬爾殊少爺！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.79,0:17:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.02,0:17:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬爾殊少爺，你不可以輸！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥！然後戰勝邪惡的心！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.98,0:18:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個膽小鬼終於出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.15,0:18:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.24,0:18:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好！怒火令他忘記了自我！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.92,0:18:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬爾殊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.66,0:18:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手！喬爾殊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經分出勝負！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你還有騎士的尊嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.14,0:18:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你便不要作無謂的戰鬥！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.27,0:18:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會放手！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你這樣戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.81,0:19:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也會變成跟Devil Gundam一樣啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SUPER MODE嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.23,0:19:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點，喬爾殊，你要冷靜！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.13,0:19:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口…！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬爾殊少爺！請你清醒一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙…！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你控制你的拳頭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.01,0:19:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要戰勝的不是米拿保
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是盤據你心內的惡魔！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.85,0:19:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要戰勝的是自己的心…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我不可讓他繼續這樣子！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.50,0:20:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，我差點忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Fighter一定要用心去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.32,0:20:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒夫爾的信物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.18,0:20:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我有資格擁有你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.72,0:20:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你便從米拿保身上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.46,0:20:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除去Devil Gundam的咀咒吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起啊，喬爾殊少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.88,0:20:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能戰勝自己心內的惡魔…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙，那全靠你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.86,0:20:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細看清楚，多蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.52,0:21:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有心的話只會產生破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.13,0:21:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，那種力量也會有好的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是看其用法罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，強大的力量是有兩面的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是『兩刃之劍』
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.01,0:21:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，你選擇哪一面？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這種人可以再當管家嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.49,0:21:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除你之外
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.76,0:21:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無人能當山度家的管家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.73,0:21:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.36,0:21:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬爾殊少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.13,0:21:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬爾殊少爺！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.74,0:21:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩人看來和好如初了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，剛才的SUPER MODE…？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.38,0:21:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.95,0:21:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的SUPER MODE
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.98,0:21:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不會那麼輕易讓我控制
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.29,0:22:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.05,0:22:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我有所領悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.99,0:22:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此，我也須要繼續修練
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.00,0:22:30.60,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便數千的日夜流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:34.99,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所到達的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.24,0:22:39.43,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨著 追求著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.90,0:22:43.00,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫步著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.24,0:22:50.15,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀人啊 在我瞳孔的深處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.63,0:22:55.85,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實搖曳著的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.05,0:23:01.16,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要如何傳達才好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.18,0:23:07.64,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓受傷的心與身體
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:11.82,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這溫暖的懷抱中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.95,0:23:17.81,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比海更深沉的睡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.59,0:23:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.54,0:23:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM FIGHT的決勝大會已近在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.21,0:23:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙卻仍未修行完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.70,0:23:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且奇波迪等人也受到了Death Army的襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.32,0:23:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟多蒙他們能否平安抵達決賽會場呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.13,0:23:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動武鬥傳G GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.60,0:23:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決賽逼近！時間限制72小時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.28,0:23:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY GO！


